							$\hat {\sigma }$
						\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M10"><mml:mover accent="true"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>σ</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mo>^</mml:mo></mml:mover></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2014_381_Article_IEq5.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> and the inverse of <inline-formula id="IEq6"><alternatives><tex-math id="M11">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
