							$\hat {\pi }$
						\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M12"><mml:mover accent="true"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>π</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mo>^</mml:mo></mml:mover></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2014_381_Article_IEq6.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, from which we can further derive <italic>m</italic>−1 special translocations to act on <inline-formula id="IEq7"><alternatives><tex-math id="M13">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
